     StyleBox["11", "InlineCode"]], "TableText",ExpressionUUID->
     "a6cd6be5-c9ff-4432-9f56-6fb2cba1b857"], Cell["\<\
the highest Laurent order subtracted in the optimal truncation\
\>", "TableText",ExpressionUUID->"26dd9b0c-8cc9-4b8a-9176-94f4eb70f8db"]},
   {Cell["", "ModInfo",ExpressionUUID->
     "98dd855f-f1d6-43a6-9d28-b12a90797916"], Cell[BoxData[
