     "22a468bd-ef00-4b68-8207-0239dd660f02"], Cell["\<\
the target relative accuracy, which sets Nsum via the nu_max law\
\>", "TableText",ExpressionUUID->"e4086d29-93ae-4b00-b2ff-e855de0dc843"]},
   {Cell["", "ModInfo",ExpressionUUID->
     "f061674a-170e-45f1-9a8d-aa40690a8269"], Cell[BoxData[
